                            <comment id="102185" author="habuma" created="Mon, 21 Apr 2014 08:37:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It appears that the big problem here is that an ExpiredAuthirizationException is created with a null provider ID. I&apos;ve fixed that (am traveling now though and will have to push later today when I get back to a real network...am using my phone for this comment). The subclass of ReconnectFilter looks roughly the same as the current ReconnectFilter code...different code but essentially the same logic. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
